HEADWORD: Avowee
<hw>A*vow`ee"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>avou⟦eacute⟧</ets>. Cf. <er>Advowee</er>, <er>Advocate</er>,
